## Data Flow

### Initialization Flow

```
User Opens Application
         │
         ▼
index.html loads
         │
         ├─→ style.css applied
         │
         ├─→ utility.js loaded
         │
         ├─→ validation.js loaded
         │
         ├─→ gemini-api-module.js loaded
         │
         └─→ scripts.js loaded
                  │
                  ▼
         DOMContentLoaded event
                  │
                  ├─→ Initialize UI
                  │
                  ├─→ Check for existing API key
                  │        │
                  │        ├─ Found → Auto-initialize GeminiAPI
                  │        │
                  │        └─ Not Found → Show config form
